<p>
<note n="0656001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0656001">（陵ハ陸ナリ。<g ref="#CB18834">󴦒</g>）</note>
<note n="0657j01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0657j01">動是業力亂想是惑性是故以下充塞之類是業果</note>
<note n="0657j02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0657j02">滋滋液也</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
